v0.1.2-tofumatt-0.1

* Moved the api_key argument into the params (and renamed it apikey)
* Allows instance default params on (use Prowl.new(params) to set defaults)
* Defaults are overridden by the params argument in Prowl.add()
* Ability to use an array of API Keys

v0.1.2

* Removed support for the old HTTP auth based API.
* Support for most recent API.
* Renamed `send` to `add`, to avoid conflicts with `Object#send`.